    <div class="content">
        <h3>Perfume puts the finishing touch to elegance.</h3>
        <p>
            Scent is our most primitive sense, it’s the closest thing to the emotional brain.
            It penetrates you.
            You love it, and you want to be part of it
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">get yours now</a>
    </div>

</section>

<!-- home section ends -->
